commit.message: docs/api/CMakeLists.txt - add a dependency to README.md

docs/api/Doxyfile.cmake - set HTML_EXTRA_STYLESHEET for doxygen.awesome

Use HTML_EXTRA_STYLESHEET, not HTML_STYLESHEET when
pointing to the doxyeng.awesome.css.

src/CMakeLists.txt - Install the Windows pdb files in the bin dir

Install the Windows pdb files in the bin (or runtime)
directory and not into the library dir.
appveyor.yml - remove. we no longer use Appveyor CI/CD

Use the doxygen-awesome.css stylesheet for web page generation

For a more beautiful set of online API documentation.

Standardize project to KDAB copyright policy

For individual files: use year of file creation
For entire project:
  remove year from the statement
  use the © where feasible

reference:
https://matija.suklje.name/how-and-why-to-properly-write-copyright-statements-in-your-code

Standardize project to KDAB copyright policy

For entire project: remove year from the statement

KDQtInstallPaths.cmake - sync to upstream

In particular, use QT_VERSION_MAJOR and remove Qt_VERSION_MAJOR

Improvements for when used as a git submodule

- don't do feature_summary, let the main repo do that
- do generate the forwarding header

.pre-commit-config.yaml - autoupdate and add a few more hooks

Add these hooks:
* check-symlinks: checks for symlinks which do not point to anything
  destroyed-symlinks:  detects symlinks which are changed to regular
  files with a content of a path which that symlink was pointing to.
* check-executables-have-shebangs:  ensures that (non-binary)
  executables have a shebang.

src/CMakeLists.txt - set VERSION and SOVERSION on the library target

The version variables are currently only passed to ecm_setup_version(),
but they need to be also specified as target properties so that CMake
installs versioned .so files on Linux, which is required for proper
distribution packaging.

Signed-off-by: Ondrej Mosnáček <omosnacek@gmail.com>
